{"title":"VS项目常用调试方法","uid":"20a581299d5041a583789bd3076d92ff","slug":"VS项目常用调试方法","date":"2022-10-31T12:37:11.000Z","updated":"2022-10-31T14:07:56.691Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/VS项目常用调试方法.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/微信图片_20221031184222.3fu2m6i2rzi0.jpg","content":"<!-- toc -->\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\">1. 打印数据</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E6%96%AD%E7%82%B9\">2. 普通断点</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%AD%E7%82%B9\">3. 条件断点</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%BF%BD%E8%B8%AA\">4. 条件追踪</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#5-%E5%8D%95%E6%AD%A5%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95\">5. 单步调试</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#6-%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86\">6. 添加监视</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- tocstop -->\n\n<hr>\n<h3><span id=\"1-打印数据\">1. 打印数据</span></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    a <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">ifdef</span> <span class=\"token expression\">_DEBUG</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"debug: i == 5, a = %d\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">endif</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//DEBUG</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a = %d\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>在VC里，debug模式的标识宏为_DEBUG, 在debug模式下该宏被定义，则打印输出i&#x3D;5时的调试信息；在release模式下则不会执行调试打印语句。注意，要尽可能详细地写出调试信息，与一般打印输出区分开。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3><span id=\"2-普通断点\">2. 普通断点</span></h3><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/QQ截图20221031211128.5h1d2t4s5m80.png\"></div>\n\n<p>在指定位置插入断点，代码执行至此便会暂停。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3><span id=\"3-条件断点\">3. 条件断点</span></h3><p>在待调试代码行，右键，插入条件断点。当程序运行至此处并且判断条件为真时，触发断点。</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/QQ截图20221031211226.6zazjwtdt7w0.png\"></div>\n\n<div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/QQ截图20221031211740.3v1c2y0n8pg0.png\"></div>\n\n<hr>\n<h3><span id=\"4-条件追踪\">4. 条件追踪</span></h3><p>我们可能想要在触发条件断点时，打印输出一些信息来帮助我们了解程序的运行状况，那么我们可以勾选<strong>操作</strong>，并添加一些代码，从而将消息记录输出到窗口。假如我们在操作中添加如下代码：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">debug<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>则会打印输出 debug: a &#x3D; 10。需要注意，当想输出某变量值时，需要用{}来进行捕获，别的字符将直接以字符格式输出。在操作中，还有一些VS为我们提供的变量可以使用，例如打印<strong>PID</strong>、<strong>函数名</strong>、<strong>堆栈</strong>等，前缀一如既往的是$，如图：</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/微信截图_20221031212829.79f3vaaezb00.png\"></div>\n\n<p>假如我们在操作中添加如下代码：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">debug<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> $PNAME <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> $TNAME <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> $FUNCTION <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>则会打印输出如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">debug<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> D<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\\VSProjects\\ServerProject\\bin\\x64\\Debug\\HelloWorld<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exe <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> 主线程 <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3><span id=\"5-单步调试\">5. 单步调试</span></h3><p>多打几个断点，让整体程序分段执行，触发断点时，鼠标悬停至变量上，可显示该变量当前的值。</p>\n<p>若想跳转至某个函数内部进行逐步分析，则需要使用“<strong>逐语句</strong>”调试，如果用“<strong>逐过程</strong>”，则不会进入函数内部调试。进入了函数之后如果想跳出，可以点“<strong>跳出</strong>”。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3><span id=\"6-添加监视\">6. 添加监视</span></h3><p>当有多个变量需要调试测值的时候，鼠标悬停看值肯定会不方便，因此可以右键点击变量，添加监视，监视窗口如下图：</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/QQ截图20221031215837.c1cu0su1780.png\"></div>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">9</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> pArr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>对于上述两行代码，若直接对arr和pArr添加监视，arr可正常被作为数组监视，而pArr则被认为是单个int变量，指向的值只有1。若想正确的监视pArr，需要右键点击pArr-&gt;快速监视，按如下输入，并点击重新计算即可：</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/Server配图/QQ截图20221031220202.2ylqza1xoy80.png\"></div>","text":" 1. 打印数据 2. 普通断点 3. 条件断点 4. 条件追踪 5. 单步调试 6. 添加监视 1. 打印数据int a = 0; for (int i = 1; i &lt;= 10; ++i) &#123; a += i; #ifdef _DEBUG if (i == 5)...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"项目记录","slug":"项目记录","count":2,"path":"api/categories/项目记录.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"VS","slug":"VS","count":2,"path":"api/tags/VS.json"},{"name":"程序调试","slug":"程序调试","count":1,"path":"api/tags/程序调试.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 打印数据</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 普通断点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 条件断点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4. 条件追踪</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5. 单步调试</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6. 添加监视</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"月下叶子","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/about/博客头像.1rm6v48dfu1s.jpg","link":"/","description":"日月东升西落，未曾负你我","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/moonlightleaf","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/leaf_in_the_moon","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"设计模式by李建忠","uid":"adf2676e452953c4451f885c2a466f48","slug":"设计模式by李建忠","date":"2022-10-15T04:54:28.000Z","updated":"2022-10-31T12:34:10.806Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/设计模式by李建忠.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/moonlightleaf/pics@master/设计模式/9b8cc7_42_Destination1_4k.44dam11au5m0.jpg","text":"《 设计模式 》by李建忠 - 一文总结(持续更新)目录 面向对象设计原则 模板方法Template Method 策略模式Strategy 观察者模式Observer &#x2F; Event 面向对象设计原则 依赖倒置原则（DIP） 高层模块（稳定）不应该依赖低层模块（变化）...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.3k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"设计模式","slug":"设计模式","count":1,"path":"api/categories/设计模式.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"设计模式","slug":"设计模式","coun